      "text": "Ad zehlahs Jerub-Ba-åls/ tas irr Gideans ag-ri/ un wiſſi Laudis/ kas pee winna bija/ un tee apmettehs pee ta Awota Aroda/ ta ka to Mi-dijaniteru Karra-Spehks win-nain prett Seemeta Puſſi/ ais to Pakalnu More Eeleija bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija us Gideanu: to Lauschu/ kas ar te-wim/ irr dauds wairak/ ne ka es tohs Midijaniterus winnu Roh-kā buhtu dewis/ ka Israēls prett mann ne leelijahs/un fakka: Man-na Rohka irr mann ispestijsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad isfauz jelle preeftsch to Lauschu Aufim/un fakki: kas bai-ligs/ un bes Drohſchibas irr/ tas laid atgreeschahs/ un steidsiu stei-dsahs no Gileadas Kalna. Tad at-greesahs no teem Laudim diwi-defimits diwituhkſtoschi / ka tur defimits tuhkſtoschi atlikke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija us Gideanu: to Lauschu wehl wiſſai daudsirr / nowedd tohs pee ta Uh-dens/ tur gribbn es tohs tew pa-baudiht / un no kuxra es us tew fazzischu : fchim buhs ar tewim eet/ tas lai ar tewim eet/bet wiſe tas/ no ka es fazzischu/ winnam buhs ar tew eet / tas lai ne eet. Un wiſch nowedde tohs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad bija tas Pulks to/ ka no fawas Rohkas pee fawa Muttes btj lakkuschi trihſfint Wihrn / bet wiſſi atlifkuschi Lau-dis bij Zeltōs ismettuschees dset-ruschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija us Gideanu: zaur scheem trihſfint Wiheem/ kas lakkuschi irr/ gri-bu es juhs ispestiht / un nodol-fchu tohs Midijaniterus taw-Rohkā/tapehz atlaid wiſsus Lau-dis/ ikkatru us fawu Weetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Laudis nehme Ba-ribu fawa Rohkā / un fawa Trummetes / bet wiſsus Israēl-Wihrus atlaide wiſsch / ikkatru us fawu Dshwoſſli/un tohs trih-fints Wihrus patureja wiſsch un toMidijaniteruKarra-Speh-bija winnam us appakschu E-leija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tanni Nakti fazzija tas KUNgs us winnu: Zellees/ nei us to Lehgeri / jo es efmu tawā Rohkā dewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tu bihstees no-eet tad no-eij tu un Purus tam-Puitis us to Lehgeri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tu dsirdeti/fo tee ru-nahs / un pehz to stiprinafees t-was Rohkas / un tad buhs ter-prett to Lehgeri zeltees / tad u-gabje wiſsch ar Puru fawu Pu\n"
    }
